description: Have dinner ready in a flash with this quick and easy garlic prawns and couscous salad recipe.
name: Garlic Prawns With Couscous Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat remaining oil in same pan over high heat. Drain prawns and cook, turning occasionally, for 3 minutes or until prawns change colour and are cooked through. Serve couscous salad topped with prawns.
